\ip Jon papiakon yo d…®war…® p…®ndakgamaŇč uŇčun yaŇč: M…®Ňčat am…®nyokon yo morap toŇč uŇčun baŇč t…®m…®gek Yesu da t…®lak gen yag…®t uŇčun baŇč mandag…®t. Do m…®r…®m, ae pakbi, ae bret, ae teŇčteŇč…®, ae wain obi, ae sipsip k…®la am…®n uŇčun dakon gen p…®ndakgamaŇč.  
