\v 1 \x - \xo 1:1 \xt Jn 17.5; 1Jn 1.1-2; PA 19.13\x*Yo morap d…®ma altaŇčakwa wasok wasog…®kon Gen uŇčun eg…®pgut. Gen uŇčun PiŇčkop gat eg…®pgumal, ae Gen iy…® PiŇčkop uŇčun.  
