\v 16 \x - \xo 11:16 \xt Mk 14.31\x*Yesu da gen yaŇč mudaŇčakwan Tomas, mani k…®nda Yayat yaŇč iy…®wit, uŇčun da paŇčdet notni d…®war…® yaŇč yoy…®g…®t, ‚ÄúNinyo k…®si uŇčun gat k…®Ňček k…®si k…®motneŇč.‚ÄĚ   
