\v 36 YaŇč aban kaŇček Juda am…®n da yaŇč yawit, ‚ÄúKab…®t. UŇčun da uŇčun am…®n do but dasi galak taŇč …®mgut.‚ÄĚ \fig Lasarus k…®moron da p…®dag…®t|alt="Raising Lazarus" src="C074.tif" size="span" loc="Location" copy="Copyright" ref="11.44" \fig*   
\p
\v 37 \x - \xo 11:37 \xt Jn 9.6-7\x*Mani am…®n d…®war…® da yawit, ‚ÄúUŇčun da dab…®l…® m…®ni am…®n aŇčm…®l…®p aban s…®Ňčtag…®t. YaŇč ag…®t, do ae nido uŇčun am…®n d…®ma aŇčpulugaŇčakwan k…®makg…®t?‚ÄĚ   
\s1 Yesu da Lasarus aban p…®dag…®t  
\p
