\v 5 ‚ÄúNak naga wain obi ae ji k…®l…®Ňčno morap. Am…®n k…®nda nagon saŇčbeŇčban nak uŇčun am…®non saŇčbekeŇč kaŇč, bam…® morapm…® tokd…®sak. Ji nak nipmaŇč degek yo k…®nda ar…®pm…® d…®ma ani. \fig Yesukon saŇčbeŇček bam…® morapm…® toni|alt="Grape vine" src="HK00112B.TIF" size="span" loc="Location" copy="Copyright" ref="15.5" \fig*   
