\v 24 Nak uŇčun da binapmon pi tapm…®m…® toŇč am…®n k…®nda da d…®ma ag…®t uŇčun baŇč ag…®m. YaŇč d…®ma ag…®m tam, yokwini dakon gen k…®nda d…®ma tosok. Mani nak da wasok tapm…®m…® toŇč ag…®m uŇčun p…®ndakgwit, mani nak gat Datno gat k…®si do nandaba yokwi tok aŇčnimaŇč.  
\v 25 \x - \xo 15:25 \xt Kap 35.19; 69.4\x*YaŇč aba gen teban papianikon gen k…®nda tosok uŇčun bam…® toŇč ag…®t. Gen uŇčun yaŇč:  
